data.name: label18.Text
data.value:
The CFBundleIdentifier identifies the application bundle. It should only contain characters in the following sets: alphanumeric (A-Z, a-z, 0-9), hyphen (-), and period (.).
If you're packaging for Mac App Store, this must match the identifier you set in Developer Certificate Utility when creating your game's App ID.

data.name: label13.Text
data.value:
Your signing certificate must be exported from Keychain, including the private key (export from My Certificates, not from All Items, and use Personal Information Exchange (.p12) as the format).
Downloading the certificate again from the Developer Certificate Utility is not sufficient, as that will not include the private key used to generate the original signing request.
